The Lagos State House of Assembly has suspended, Hon. Moshood Oshun Lagos Mainland 2 and Hon. Adewale Raheem Ibeju Lekki 2 for gross misconduct and activities that undermines the sanctity of the house.

The Speaker, Rt.Hon.Mudashiru Obasa while announcing the suspension notes that discipline is key for the protection of the sanctity of the house against insubordination.

Obasa invoke house rules 68,74,4a,b,2 and 3 to enforce the suspension.

